<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="Plano Estratégico Nexora — diagnóstico completo com causa raiz, leitura sistêmica e plano de ação priorizado para vendedores Amazon." />
  <title>Nexora Intelligence — Plano Estratégico</title>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#08080f;
      --surface:#0d1018;
      --surface2:#121620;
      --border:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      --border2:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      --blue:#1a4a8a;
      --blue2:#2a6ab0;
      --blue-light:#4a90d9;
      --red:#c0392b;
      --red2:#e84040;
      --green:#1a8a3a;
      --green2:#22a847;
      --text:#e8edf2;
      --gray:#8a9ab0;
      --muted:#6a7a8a;
      --muted2:#3a4a5a;
      --shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.22);
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{
      background:var(--bg);
      color:var(--text);
      font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;
      font-size:16px;
      line-height:1.65;
      overflow-x:hidden;
    }

    body::before{
      content:'';
      position:fixed;
      inset:0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% -10%, rgba(26,74,138,0.15) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 10%, rgba(74,144,217,0.08) 0%, transparent 18%);
      pointer-events:none;
      z-index:0;
    }

    .noise{
      position:fixed;
      inset:0;
      pointer-events:none;
      z-index:0;
      opacity:.025;
      background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    }

    .scan-lines{
      position:fixed;
      inset:0;
      pointer-events:none;
      z-index:0;
      opacity:.05;
      background:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,.04) 0, rgba(255,255,255,.04) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 6px);
      mask-image:radial-gradient(circle at center, black 40%, transparent 95%);
    }

    .wrap{max-width:1140px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px;position:relative;z-index:1}
    .wrap-sm{max-width:780px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px;position:relative;z-index:1}

    nav{
      padding:22px 0;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      position:sticky;
      top:0;
      background:rgba(8,8,15,.92);
      backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
      z-index:100;
    }

    .nav-inner{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px}

    .brand{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:12px;
      text-decoration:none;
      color:var(--text);
    }

    .brand-mark{
      width:40px;
      height:40px;
      border-radius:12px;
      background:linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(74,144,217,.18), rgba(232,64,64,.08));
      border:1px solid var(--border2);
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      box-shadow:inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:-.04em;
    }

    .brand-copy{display:flex;flex-direction:column;line-height:1.1}
    .brand-copy strong{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.04em}
    .brand-copy span{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em}

    .nav-actions{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}

    .btn-primary,.btn-ghost,.btn-green{
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-size:13px;
      font-weight:700;
      padding:14px 26px;
      border-radius:10px;
      text-decoration:none;
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      gap:8px;
      letter-spacing:.04em;
      transition:all .2s ease;
      cursor:pointer;
      border:none;
    }

    .btn-primary{background:var(--red);color:#fff}
    .btn-primary:hover{background:var(--red2);transform:translateY(-1px)}

    .btn-ghost{
      background:transparent;
      color:var(--gray);
      border:1px solid var(--border2);
    }
    .btn-ghost:hover{color:var(--text);border-color:var(--blue2)}

    .btn-green{background:var(--green);color:#fff}
    .btn-green:hover{background:var(--green2);transform:translateY(-1px)}

    .hero{
      padding:96px 0 74px;
      position:relative;
    }

    .hero-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr;
      gap:40px;
      align-items:center;
    }

    .hero-tag,.section-tag,.mini-tag{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:8px;
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-size:10px;
      font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:.16em;
      color:var(--blue-light);
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    .hero-tag{
      margin-bottom:22px;
      padding:8px 16px;
      border:1px solid rgba(74,144,217,.2);
      border-radius:999px;
      background:rgba(74,144,217,.06);
    }

    .hero-tag-dot{
      width:5px;
      height:5px;
      border-radius:50%;
      background:var(--red2);
    }

    h1{
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-size:clamp(40px,5.7vw,72px);
      line-height:1.02;
      letter-spacing:-.04em;
      font-weight:800;
      margin-bottom:20px;
    }

    h2{
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,46px);
      line-height:1.1;
      letter-spacing:-.03em;
      font-weight:800;
      margin:14px 0 14px;
    }

    .accent{color:var(--blue-light)}
    .red{color:var(--red2)}

    .hero-sub,.section-sub{
      color:var(--gray);
      font-size:18px;
      font-weight:300;
      line-height:1.8;
    }

    .hero-sub{max-width:620px;margin-bottom:34px}
    .section-sub{max-width:620px}

    .hero-ctas{
      display:flex;
      gap:12px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      margin-bottom:22px;
    }

    .hero-note{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)}

    .hero-card{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(18,22,32,.86), rgba(13,16,24,.96));
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:20px;
      padding:28px;
      position:relative;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .hero-card::before{
      content:'';
      position:absolute;
      inset:auto -20% 65% auto;
      width:220px;
      height:220px;
      border-radius:50%;
      background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(74,144,217,.18) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .hero-card::after{
      content:'';
      position:absolute;
      inset:0;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(74,144,217,.05), transparent 45%, rgba(232,64,64,.05));
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .mini-tag{position:relative;z-index:1}
    .price-line{
      display:flex;
      align-items:end;
      gap:12px;
      margin:10px 0 18px;
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
    }

    .price{
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-size:48px;
      line-height:1;
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:-.04em;
    }

    .price-label{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted)}

    .hero-list{
      list-style:none;
      display:grid;
      gap:12px;
      margin:22px 0 28px;
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
    }

    .hero-list li{
      display:flex;
      gap:12px;
      align-items:flex-start;
      font-size:14px;
      color:var(--gray);
    }

    .check{
      width:20px;
      height:20px;
      flex:0 0 20px;
      border-radius:6px;
      background:rgba(74,144,217,.12);
      border:1px solid rgba(74,144,217,.18);
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      color:var(--blue-light);
      font-size:12px;
      font-weight:700;
      margin-top:1px;
    }

    .trust-mini{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
      gap:10px;
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
    }

    .trust-mini .cell{
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:12px;
      padding:14px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.015);
    }

    .trust-mini strong{
      display:block;
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-size:22px;
    }

    .trust-mini span{
      font-size:12px;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .section{padding:82px 0}

    .stats-bar{
      border-top:1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      padding:24px 0;
      margin-top:8px;
    }

    .stats-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
      gap:18px;
    }

    .stat-item{text-align:center}
    .stat-item strong{
      display:block;
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-size:28px;
      font-weight:800;
    }

    .stat-item span{
      font-size:12px;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .pain-grid,.deliver-grid,.results-grid,.faq-grid{
      display:grid;
      gap:14px;
      margin-top:42px;
    }

    .pain-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}
    .deliver-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}
    .results-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}
    .faq-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}

    .card{
      background:var(--surface);
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:16px;
      padding:24px;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
      transition:transform .2s ease,border-color .2s ease, background .2s ease;
    }

    .card:hover{
      transform:translateY(-2px);
      border-color:var(--border2);
    }

    .card-top{
      position:absolute;
      top:0;
      left:0;
      right:0;
      height:2px;
      background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--blue),var(--blue-light));
    }

    .card h3{
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-size:16px;
      margin-bottom:8px;
    }

    .card p{
      font-size:14px;
      color:var(--muted);
      line-height:1.7;
    }

    .icon-badge{
      width:38px;
      height:38px;
      border-radius:10px;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      margin-bottom:14px;
      background:rgba(74,144,217,.12);
      border:1px solid rgba(74,144,217,.18);
      color:var(--blue-light);
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-weight:700;
    }

    .process-wrap{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:.95fr 1.05fr;
      gap:48px;
      align-items:start;
    }

    .steps{
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      gap:0;
      margin-top:34px;
    }

    .step{
      display:flex;
      gap:22px;
      padding:24px 0;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .step:last-child{border-bottom:none}

    .step-num{
      width:38px;
      height:38px;
      border-radius:10px;
      flex:0 0 38px;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      background:var(--surface2);
      border:1px solid var(--border2);
      color:var(--blue-light);
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-size:11px;
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:.06em;
    }

    .step-title{
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-size:16px;
      margin-bottom:6px;
    }

    .step-desc{
      font-size:14px;
      color:var(--muted);
      line-height:1.7;
    }

    .featured{
      margin-top:48px;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(18,22,32,.92), rgba(13,16,24,1));
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:22px;
      padding:32px;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .featured::before{
      content:'';
      position:absolute;
      inset:-40px auto auto -40px;
      width:200px;
      height:200px;
      border-radius:50%;
      background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(74,144,217,.18) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .featured-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      gap:14px;
      margin:28px 0 24px;
    }

    .feature-item{
      display:flex;
      gap:12px;
      align-items:flex-start;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.015);
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:14px;
      padding:16px;
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
    }

    .feature-item strong{
      display:block;
      font-size:14px;
      margin-bottom:4px;
    }

    .feature-item p{
      font-size:13px;
      color:var(--muted);
      line-height:1.65;
    }

    .featured-actions{
      display:flex;
      gap:12px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      margin-top:18px;
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
    }

    .featured-note{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:12px;
      margin-top:14px;
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
    }

    .comparison{
      margin-top:22px;
      overflow:auto;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:16px;
      background:var(--surface);
    }

    table{
      width:100%;
      border-collapse:collapse;
      min-width:720px;
    }

    th,td{
      padding:18px 18px;
      text-align:left;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      font-size:14px;
    }

    th{
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-size:13px;
      letter-spacing:.03em;
      color:var(--text);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.015);
    }

    td{color:var(--gray)}
    tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}

    .pill{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      padding:6px 10px;
      border-radius:999px;
      font-size:11px;
      font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:.04em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      background:var(--surface2);
      border:1px solid var(--border2);
      color:var(--gray);
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
    }

    .pill.highlight{
      color:#fff;
      background:rgba(74,144,217,.18);
      border-color:rgba(74,144,217,.28);
    }

    .testimonial{
      margin-top:26px;
      padding:24px;
      border-radius:16px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.015);
    }

    .testimonial p{
      font-size:16px;
      color:var(--text);
      line-height:1.8;
      margin-bottom:14px;
    }

    .testimonial strong{
      display:block;
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    .testimonial span{
      font-size:12px;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .faq-item details{
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:14px;
      padding:18px 18px;
      background:var(--surface);
      transition:border-color .2s ease;
    }

    .faq-item details[open]{
      border-color:var(--border2);
    }

    .faq-item summary{
      list-style:none;
      cursor:pointer;
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-size:15px;
      font-weight:700;
      color:var(--text);
      position:relative;
      padding-right:28px;
    }

    .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}
    .faq-item summary::after{
      content:'+';
      position:absolute;
      right:0;
      top:0;
      color:var(--blue-light);
      font-size:18px;
      font-weight:700;
    }

    .faq-item details[open] summary::after{content:'–'}
    .faq-item p{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:14px;
      margin-top:12px;
      line-height:1.75;
    }

    .cta-section{
      padding:0 0 88px;
    }

    .cta-box{
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      background:var(--surface);
      border-radius:22px;
      padding:52px 34px;
      text-align:center;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .cta-box::before{
      content:'';
      position:absolute;
      inset:auto 50% -80px auto;
      width:220px;
      height:220px;
      border-radius:50%;
      transform:translateX(50%);
      background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(74,144,217,.14) 0%, transparent 72%);
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .cta-actions{
      display:flex;
      justify-content:center;
      gap:12px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      margin-top:26px;
    }

    .inline-proof{
      font-size:12px;
      color:var(--muted);
      margin-top:16px;
    }

    footer{
      border-top:1px solid var(--border);
      padding:28px 0 36px;
    }

    .footer-inner{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:16px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .footer-copy{
      font-size:12px;
      color:var(--muted2);
    }

    .footer-links{
      display:flex;
      gap:20px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .footer-links a{
      text-decoration:none;
      color:var(--muted2);
      font-size:13px;
      transition:color .2s ease;
    }

    .footer-links a:hover{color:var(--gray)}

    .reveal{
      opacity:0;
      transform:translateY(18px);
      transition:opacity .65s ease, transform .65s ease;
    }

    .reveal.is-visible{
      opacity:1;
      transform:none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px){
      .hero-grid,
      .process-wrap,
      .featured-grid,
      .faq-grid{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .pain-grid,
      .deliver-grid,
      .results-grid{
        grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      }

      .stats-grid{
        grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px){
      .pain-grid,
      .deliver-grid,
      .results-grid,
      .trust-mini,
      .stats-grid{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .hero{padding:72px 0 48px}
      .section{padding:66px 0}
      .step{flex-direction:column;gap:12px}
      .nav-actions{display:none}
      .cta-box{padding:40px 22px}
      h1{font-size:38px}
      h2{font-size:30px}
      .hero-sub,.section-sub{font-size:16px}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="noise"></div>
  <div class="scan-lines"></div>

  <nav>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="nav-inner">
        <a href="/" class="brand">
          <div class="brand-mark">N</div>
          <div class="brand-copy">
            <strong>NEXORA INTELLIGENCE</strong>
            <span>Plano Estratégico</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <div class="nav-actions">
          <a href="#detalhes" class="btn-ghost">Ver detalhes</a>
          <a href="#comprar" class="btn-primary">Quero meu diagnóstico</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <section class="hero" id="top">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div class="reveal">
            <div class="hero-tag">
              <span class="hero-tag-dot"></span>
              <span>Oferta principal da Nexora</span>
            </div>

            <h1>
              Seu produto não está travado por <span class="red">falta de esforço.</span><br>
              Está travado por <span class="accent">falta de direção.</span>
            </h1>

            <p class="hero-sub">
              O Plano Estratégico da Nexora foi criado para identificar a causa raiz da sua performance na Amazon e mostrar exatamente onde mexer primeiro.
            </p>

            <div class="hero-ctas">
              <a href="#comprar" class="btn-primary">Comprar plano estratégico</a>
              <a href="#como-funciona" class="btn-ghost">Como funciona</a>
            </div>

            <p class="hero-note">
              Diagnóstico completo + relatório estruturado + call estratégica.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-card reveal">
            <span class="mini-tag">Plano principal</span>

            <div class="price-line">
              <div class="price">R$ 1.297</div>
              <div class="price-label">pagamento único</div>
            </div>

            <ul class="hero-list">
              <li><span class="check">✓</span><span>Diagnóstico sistêmico da operação Amazon</span></li>
              <li><span class="check">✓</span><span>Relatório com causa raiz e leitura estratégica</span></li>
              <li><span class="check">✓</span><span>Call explicativa para orientar as prioridades</span></li>
              <li><span class="check">✓</span><span>Plano de ação claro, sem execução operacional</span></li>
            </ul>

            <div class="trust-mini">
              <div class="cell">
                <strong>1</strong>
                <span>diagnóstico completo</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cell">
                <strong>3</strong>
                <span>camadas principais de análise</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cell">
                <strong>1</strong>
                <span>call estratégica inclusa</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cell">
                <strong>100%</strong>
                <span>foco em clareza e direção</span>
              </div>
